{"tid":1958204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獨媒: 【2020年，香港人的清明節】","createTime":"2020-04-04T12:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T13:35:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7397549a9249022f24e782cfb038060fcdbdfb4e","tid":1958204,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T12:41:58.000Z","msg":"【2020年，香港人的清明節】<br />\n<br />\n今日清明節，不少人到位於羅湖的沙嶺公墓拜祭。<br />\n<br />\n這裡安葬的都是無人認領的屍體。來拜祭的人在每一個沒有名字、只有編號和日期的墓碑前，放下一束白花或上香。石碑前還有其他祭品，包括工地頭盔、黃色雨傘、紀錄反送中抗爭的書籍等。<br />\n<br />\n在地上，有人畫了指向墳場方向的箭嘴，寫上「拜手足」數字；在樹上，有人掛起「光復香港，時代革命」的旗幟。 @ 沙嶺墳場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/91896739_2860022414034778_6688518137307987968_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=9e2e56&amp;_nc_ohc=uSxFoOkIa1oAX9atudd&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=990834131b00f225d38a47384fd05eeb&amp;oe=5EAD335A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F91896739_2860022414034778_6688518137307987968_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D9e2e56%26_nc_ohc%3DuSxFoOkIa1oAX9atudd%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D990834131b00f225d38a47384fd05eeb%26oe%3D5EAD335A&h=a2f50cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/91940794_2860022504034769_3479280872513863680_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_sid=9e2e56&amp;_nc_ohc=0JZVCm03-G0AX-Ms8va&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=7e0f4fd442b27fa90509c73c41bc30c7&amp;oe=5EACB216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F91940794_2860022504034769_3479280872513863680_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_sid%3D9e2e56%26_nc_ohc%3D0JZVCm03-G0AX-Ms8va%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D7e0f4fd442b27fa90509c73c41bc30c7%26oe%3D5EACB216&h=f106c612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/91627185_2860022587368094_1713131058439913472_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=9e2e56&amp;_nc_ohc=tFpDoS06bHwAX-UtpUN